<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 09:14:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>政府数据显示，印度4月至9月钢铁进口量以中国为首</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-april-sept-steel-imports-led-by-china-govt-data-shows-2024-11-08/</link><description>路透社周五查阅的临时政府数据显示，印度 4 月至 9 月期间的钢铁进口主要来自中国，而这个南亚国家仍然是该合金的净进口国。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 09:06:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/indias-april-sept-steel-imports-led-by-china-govt-data-shows-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>东南亚为逃离特朗普对中国关税的工厂做准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/southeast-asia-prepares-factories-fleeing-trump-tariffs-china-2024-11-08/</link><description>该地区工业园区开发商表示，企业一直在将工厂从中国迁往东南亚，预计唐纳德·特朗普如果重新入主白宫，将对北京征收高额关税，随着他赢得大选，这一举措将加速。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 09:02:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/southeast-asia-prepares-factories-fleeing-trump-tariffs-china-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国派副总理出席巴库COP29气候峰会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-sends-vice-premier-cop29-climate-summit-baku-2024-11-08/</link><description>外交部发言人周五表示，中国副总理丁薛祥将于下周前往阿塞拜疆首都巴库出席第二十九届联合国气候变化框架公约(COP29)峰会。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 08:55:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-sends-vice-premier-cop29-climate-summit-baku-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>历峰集团预计美国业务将回升，选举不确定性现已消除</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-expects-pick-up-us-with-election-uncertainty-now-out-way-2024-11-08/</link><description>由于本周总统大选后的选举前不确定性已经消除，历峰集团的美国业务可能会得到提振，尽管现在判断唐纳德·特朗普领导下的关税上调将如何影响这家奢侈品公司还为时过早。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 08:39:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/richemont-expects-pick-up-us-with-election-uncertainty-now-out-way-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>随着欧盟碳关税的临近，新的绿色钢铁公司可能会获得回报</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/new-green-steel-firms-could-reap-rewards-eu-carbon-tariffs-loom-2024-11-08/</link><description>在泰国东海岸，正在计划建造一座电弧炉，该电弧炉将向欧洲提供绿色钢铁，并受益于有争议的新规则，该规则将迫使买家支付高碳进口关税。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 07:54:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/new-green-steel-firms-could-reap-rewards-eu-carbon-tariffs-loom-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>报告称，Stellantis 将从 11 月底起将 Mirafiori 工厂再停产一个月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-halt-production-mirafiori-another-month-end-nov-report-says-2024-11-08/</link><description>据每日 MF 周五援引两位消息人士的话报道，汽车制造商 Stellantis 将于 12 月再次停止位于都灵 Mirafiori 工厂的汽车生产，至少再停产一个月。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 07:47:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-halt-production-mirafiori-another-month-end-nov-report-says-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普政府如何真正帮助中国和日本市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/how-asias-markets-could-actually-benefit-trump-white-house-2024-11-08/</link><description>随着唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫，亚洲甚至中国正在形成出人意料的弹性投资市场，基金经理乐观地认为该地区能够比欧洲更好地承受关税。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 07:04:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/how-asias-markets-could-actually-benefit-trump-white-house-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国特使表示，随着中美对抗迫在眉睫，贸易战没有赢家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/no-winners-trade-industrial-wars-chinas-ambassador-us-says-2024-11-08/</link><description>中国驻美国高级特使表示，关税或贸易战、科技或工业战争没有赢家，因为唐纳德·特朗普的总统选举胜利引发了与中国再次发生激烈对抗的担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 06:33:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/no-winners-trade-industrial-wars-chinas-ambassador-us-says-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>卡地亚母公司历峰集团销售额因中国经济低迷而下滑，但珠宝却大放异彩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/cartier-owner-richemont-reports-1-dip-q3-sales-2024-11-08/</link><description>卡地亚 (Cartier) 珠宝母公司历峰集团 (Richemont) 周五公布季度销售额下滑，该奢侈品集团在其他地区的增长在很大程度上抵消了中国严峻的形势。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 06:19:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/cartier-owner-richemont-reports-1-dip-q3-sales-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>联合国警惕地等待唐纳德·特朗普重新掌权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/united-nations-warily-awaits-donald-trumps-return-power-2024-11-08/</link><description>联合国一直在为唐纳德·特朗普可能的回归以及削减美国的资金和与世界组织的接触做好准备，这可能会在他担任总统的第二个任期内出现。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 06:09:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/united-nations-warily-awaits-donald-trumps-return-power-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普之后，德国政治危机席卷工业界</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/after-trump-german-political-crisis-engulfs-industry-2024-11-08/</link><description>支出和行业政策方面持续数月的紧张局势逐渐结束。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 06:08:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/after-trump-german-political-crisis-engulfs-industry-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>准备好了没？中国如何应对第二次特朗普冲击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ready-or-not-how-china-scrambled-counter-second-trump-shock-2024-11-08/</link><description>八年前，唐纳德·特朗普首次入主白宫后，惊慌失措的中国领导人对他的关税和激烈言辞进行了武力回应，导致一场贸易战，导致全球最大经济体之间的关系跌至多年来的低点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 06:03:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ready-or-not-how-china-scrambled-counter-second-trump-shock-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾总统签署新法律维护南海权利和主权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-president-signs-new-laws-assert-south-china-sea-rights-sovereignty-2024-11-08/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周五签署了两项法律，旨在加强该国的海洋主张并巩固其领土完整，因为与中国在南海争议地区的紧张局势持续存在。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 05:20:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-president-signs-new-laws-assert-south-china-sea-rights-sovereignty-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>印度尼西亚总理普拉博沃启程前往中国进行多国访问</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesias-prabowo-heads-china-start-multi-country-trip-2024-11-08/</link><description>印度尼西亚新任领导人普拉博沃·苏比安托周五启程前往中国，开始他就任总统后的首次国际访问，拉开了访问美国、英国和南美的序幕，出席亚太经合组织和二十国集团峰会。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 04:26:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesias-prabowo-heads-china-start-multi-country-trip-2024-11-08/</guid></item><item><title>奢侈鞋履制造商马诺洛·伯拉尼克 (Manolo Blahnik) 经过 22 年的法律纠纷后进入中国市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/luxury-shoemaker-manolo-blahnik-enters-china-market-after-22-year-legal-tussle-2024-11-08/</link><description>电视剧《欲望都市》中经常穿着的高端鞋履品牌Manolo Blahnik拥有众多明星粉丝，经过22年的名称合法权斗争，该品牌在中国大陆开设了第一家专卖店。</description><pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 03:26:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/luxury-shoemaker-manolo-blahnik-enters-china-market-after-22-year-legal-tussle-2024-11-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>